OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,FCampaigners have welcomed the 31 year
OL,8,Fsentence handed down to the killer of
OL,9,FNatalie McNally but are calling for a
OL,10,Fspecific crime of femicide to deter
OL,11,Fperpetrators of violence against women
OL,12,Fand girls.
OL,14,FStephen McCullagh murdered his
OL,15,Fpregnant partner in her home in Lurgan
OL,16,Fin 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
