OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1780920676
OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,FThe 36-year-old, of Woodland Gardens
OL,8,Fin Lisburn, was found guilty in March.
OL,9,FHis jail term is one of the longest
OL,10,Fever handed down for murder in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FPassing sentence at Belfast Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Wednesday, trial judge Mr
OL,15,FJustice Kinney said McCullagh's
OL,16,Fculpability had been assessed as
OL,17,F"extremely high", describing the
OL,18,Fmurder as a "brutal and frenzied
OL,19,Fattack".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@PO]zD@MOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
