OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1780920676
OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,FCampaigners have welcomed the sentence
OL,8,Fbut feel that more needs to be done to
OL,9,Fprotect women and girls.
OL,11,FSonya McMullan, Women's Aid said:
OL,12,F"We're calling for a specific offense
OL,13,Fof femicide within the sentencing bill
OL,14,Fthat's going through the Justice
OL,15,FCommittee at the moment, and calling
OL,16,Ffor a minimum life tariff of 30 years
OL,17,Ffor specific crimes of femicide
OL,18,Fbecause we need to call it out.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1780920676
OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,F"But we do think that this sends a
OL,8,Fstrong message, and it really frames
OL,9,Fthe sentence. Even the comments by the
OL,10,Fjudge were very clear for the public
OL,11,Fto instill more public confidence in
OL,12,Fsentencing and more understanding of
OL,13,Fit as well.
OL,15,FElaine Crory, from Raise Your Voice
OL,16,Fsays: "Now we have a legal system
OL,17,Fprepared to and ready to take very
OL,18,Fseriously these kinds of cases.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1780920676
OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,F"The sentence is very high, but
OL,8,Fappropriate to the level of
OL,9,Fpremeditation and everything else that
OL,10,Fwent into it, and the attempts to
OL,11,Fobfuscate and to set police on a
OL,12,Fdifferent course.
OL,14,F"The lack of remorse and so forth. But
OL,15,Fwe really need, people to learn from
OL,16,Fthis, that we're setting down a
OL,17,Fmarker. This is how we stand now on
OL,18,Ffemicide and on violence against women
OL,19,Fand girls."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
