CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1780920676
OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,FMcCullough tried to frame Natalie's ex-
OL,8,Fboyfriend and said he was on a live
OL,9,FYouTube stream at the time of the
OL,10,Fkilling. But the police discovered his
OL,11,Falibi was pre-recorded, putting it to
OL,12,Fhim in custody interviews, which he
OL,13,Fdenied.
OL,15,FThe judge described the killing as
OL,16,F"brutal and senseless, planned in
OL,17,Fremorseful detail, cold-blooded, and
OL,18,Fcalculated."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
