OL,3,CCampaigners welcome McCullagh
OL,4,Csentencing but say sentencing laws
OL,5,Cneed reform
OL,7,FBy contrast, Mr. Justice Kinney
OL,8,Fpraised the McNallys for their
OL,9,Fexemplary demeanor and said they were
OL,10,Fan essential part of getting justice
OL,11,Ffor Natalie, who was described as
OL,12,Fstrong, loving, independent,
OL,13,Fintelligent, passionate, and funny.
OL,15,FStephen McCullough may now be serving
OL,16,F31 years behind bars, but for the
OL,17,FMcNally's, their life sentence will
OL,18,Fnever end.
